data.title: Clarence Ray Barnett Obituary 2022

data.text:
Clarence Ray Barnett, 64, passed away Thursday, June 16, 2022, at 11:05 PM. Clarence is proceeded in death by his father, Lee D. Barnett; mother, Bernice K. Fultz; and grandson Kevin X. Summers. He is survived by his wife of 34 years Kelly Barnett; sister, Chrystal J. Barnett; brother, Christopher E. (Emily) Fultz; and stepfather Grover E. Fultz; Children Timothy (Charlene) Barnett, Christina (Josh) Tucker, and Michelle (Eric) Summers of W.V., Katherine L.M. (Ryan) Barnett, William Barnett, Andrew Barnett, Beverly Barnett of Ohio, and his 14 grandchildren.

He was loved deeply and will be missed.

The family will receive friends Wednesday, June 22, 2022, from 12:00 Noon-1:00 PM at the RADER-McDONALD-TIDD FUNERAL HOME, 1355 W. MAIN STREET, WEST JEFFERSON, OH, 43162.
